1. Set text editor's tab function to 2 spaces.
2. # is used to comment code
3. Always use snake_case to formate a method, variable or file. Lowercase, spaces are underscores _ .
4. Constants are always deonted with all uppercase letters. e.g. FOUR = 4
5. When working with do... end, use {} when entire code expression fits ONE line.
5. Always use CamelCase when naming classes. No spaces and capitalize every word.